<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1317599-god-speaks-to-human-consciousness-through">God speaks to human consciousness through the presence of the Christ ... is there any other way?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1317599'><a id="like_count_community_question_1317599" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1317599?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">2 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F15015.Conversations_with_God">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1317599-god-speaks-to-human-consciousness-through">3 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1317599-god-speaks-to-human-consciousness-through">See all 6 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/64120342-pooja"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_100x100-259587f1619f5253426a4fa6fb508831.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/64120342-pooja">Pooja</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Any way is God&apos;s way. God speaks to human consciousness through ways that are beyond limits. If the presence of Christ is the way for you, so be it, t<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Any way is God's way. God speaks to human consciousness through ways that are beyond limits. If the presence of Christ is the way for you, so be it, that is the way God is speaking to you. If you feel the same with the presence of any other form, perhaps a Hindu God or a Mosque you pass by, then so be it, God is speaking to you. It does not matter what way is chosen, ways can be several, your consciousness is all it takes for you to hear God and observe the messages for you.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
